---
title: Parmesan-Crumbed Chicken Strips with Roasted Potatoes & Smokey Aioli
description: We're upping the ante on classic crumbed chicken by combining Parmesan with panko breadcrumbs for plenty of flavour and crunch, then throwing in a tantalising smokey aioli for dipping.
